EventDescription.SourceString: Rumors of a dangerous beast roaming the northern edges of the world are germinating. A magic wielding beast of frozen flesh has been reported devouring innocents and freezing entire townships solid. Though the rumor is questionable, the body count is certainly not. Investigate the truth of this rumor and find out for yourself what’s going on. Is there really a magical being terrorizing the populace?
